Research question
How have translator–author within the Governor General’s Literary Awards (1959–present) shaped the geographic and linguistic circulation of Canadian literature?

Subject:
Canadian Literary Mobility Across English–French Linguistic Borders.

Topic:
Translator–author networks within the Governor General’s Literary Awards (1959–present), focusing on how French–English translations move through Canada’s major cultural hubs.

Goal:
To map and analyze the long-term flow of translations, who translates whom, and in which direction. From these regions, in order to understand how literary influence, linguistic power, and cultural circulation shift between Quebec and the rest of Canada over time.

query:
SELECT DISTINCT
  ?person ?personLabel
  ?occupationLabel
  ?citizenshipLabel
  ?ethnicLabel
  ?award ?awardLabel
  ?awardDate
  ?work ?workLabel
  ?workLangLabel
  ?birthPlace ?birthPlaceLabel ?birth_coords
  ?residence ?residenceLabel ?res_coords
  ?nativeLanguageLabel
  ?spokenLanguageLabel
  ?category
WHERE {
  # Award statements with qualifiers for date and work
  ?person p:P166 ?awardStmt.
  ?awardStmt ps:P166 ?award.

  # Limit to Governor General's Literary Awards family via "part of" (P361); allow nested parts
  ?award wdt:P361* wd:Q3405963.

  OPTIONAL { ?awardStmt pq:P585 ?awardDate. }
  OPTIONAL { ?awardStmt pq:P1686 ?work. }

  # Person attributes
  OPTIONAL { ?person wdt:P106 ?occupation. }
  OPTIONAL { ?person wdt:P27 ?citizenship. }
  OPTIONAL { ?person wdt:P172 ?ethnic. }
  OPTIONAL { ?person wdt:P103 ?nativeLanguage. }
  OPTIONAL { ?person wdt:P1412 ?spokenLanguage. }

  # Geography: birthplace and residence with coordinates
  OPTIONAL {
    ?person wdt:P19 ?birthPlace.
    OPTIONAL { ?birthPlace wdt:P625 ?birth_coords. }
  }
  OPTIONAL {
    ?person wdt:P551 ?residence.
    OPTIONAL { ?residence wdt:P625 ?res_coords. }
  }

  # Work language
  OPTIONAL { ?work wdt:P407 ?workLang. }

  # Time filter: 1959–present (when a date qualifier exists)
  FILTER( !BOUND(?awardDate) || (YEAR(?awardDate) >= 1959) )

  # Language/identity categorization
  BIND(
    IF(
      EXISTS { ?person wdt:P172 ?eg FILTER(?eg IN (wd:Q3343315, wd:Q160746, wd:Q42106)) }, "Indigenous",
      IF(
        EXISTS { { ?person wdt:P103 wd:Q150 } UNION { ?person wdt:P1412 wd:Q150 } UNION { ?work wdt:P407 wd:Q150 } }, "French",
        IF(
          EXISTS { { ?person wdt:P103 wd:Q1860 } UNION { ?person wdt:P1412 wd:Q1860 } UNION { ?work wdt:P407 wd:Q1860 } }, "English",
          "Other"
        )
      )
    ) AS ?category
  )

  # Labels
  SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en,fr". }
}
ORDER BY ASC(?awardDate) ASC(?personLabel)
LIMIT 5000

